            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1444936/">文艺男青年与文艺女青年的生死大战</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1444936_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1444936">
                    <div class="short-content">

